{"id":3346,"date":"2023-08-11T13:18:32","date_gmt":"2023-08-11T06:18:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/?p=3346"},"modified":"2023-10-12T16:32:41","modified_gmt":"2023-10-12T09:32:41","slug":"di-du-hoc-dai-loan-nen-chon-truong-nao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/di-du-hoc-dai-loan-nen-chon-truong-nao\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e0i loan n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o?"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\"><strong>I. Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ecdc sinh qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf nh\u1edd v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c cao c\u1ea5p, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o? Khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n 5 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 h\u1eefu \u00edch gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi &#8220;<strong>du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o?<\/strong>&#8220;.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">II. D<b>u h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o?<\/b><\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00e0i Loan (National Taiwan University)<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00e0i Loan (NTU) l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng cao trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. NTU n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p cho sinh vi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">NTU cung c\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, bao g\u1ed3m Khoa h\u1ecdc X\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, Kinh t\u1ebf, Khoa h\u1ecdc, K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, Y h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3349\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3349\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3349 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/8-3.png\" alt=\"du-hoc-dai-loan-nen-chon-truong-nao\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/8-3.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/8-3-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3349\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Du h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e0i loan n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o?<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Tsing Hua (National Tsing Hua University)<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Tsing Hua (NTHU) c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan. NTHU n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao trong c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c Khoa h\u1ecdc, K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 Ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sinh vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i NTHU c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt \u0111a d\u1ea1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3350\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3350\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3350\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/9-3.png\" alt=\"Tsing-Hua\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/9-3.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/9-3-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3350\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Tsing Hua<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Chung Hsing (National Chung Hsing University)<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Chung Hsing (NCHU) n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c N\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 Khoa h\u1ecdc T\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. NCHU c\u0169ng cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Khoa h\u1ecdc X\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 Kinh t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">NCHU c\u00f3 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng th\u00ed nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3351\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3351\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3351\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/10-1.png\" alt=\"chung-hsing\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/10-1.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/10-1-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3351\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Chung Hsing<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM:<\/strong> <a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-admin\/post.php?post=3346&amp;action=edit\">\u0110i du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ea7n bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n?<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4. \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Sun Yat-sen (National Sun Yat-sen University)<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Sun Yat-sen (NSYSU) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cao trong c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c Kinh t\u1ebf, Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd Kinh doanh, Khoa h\u1ecdc X\u00e3 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">NSYSU c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111a qu\u1ed1c gia, thu h\u00fat sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1eeb kh\u1eafp n\u01a1i tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3352\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3352\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3352\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/11.png\" alt=\"Sun-Yat-sen\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/11.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/11-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3352\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Sun Yat-sen<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">5. \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Taiwan (National Taiwan University)<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Taiwan (NTNU) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o. NTNU n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u v\u1ec1 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, Ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 Ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sinh vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i NTNU c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u1ea1i kh\u00f3a, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 thao, t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 s\u1ed1ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3353\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3353\" style=\"width: 696px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3353\" src=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/12-1.png\" alt=\"quoc-gia-taiwan\" width=\"696\" height=\"392\" srcset=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/12-1.png 696w, https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/12-1-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3353\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia Taiwan<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><strong>III. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p <\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan, c\u1ea7n xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 sau:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc: N\u1eafm v\u1eefng c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp: Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh: T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh d\u00e0nh cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i t\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p: Xem x\u00e9t s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sau khi du h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0i Loan, mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho sinh vi\u00ean qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. H\u00e3y xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngay h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du h\u1ecdc \u0110\u00e0i Loan c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/duhocsmartway.vn\/\">Smart Way<\/a>. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Fanpage:\u00a0<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/duhocsmartway\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener